Package: abasequence
Title: Coding ABA patterns for sequence data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Andrew", "Pilny", , "andy.pilny@uky.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6603-5490"))
Description: The abasequence package provides a suite of functions for analyzing sequences of events. It allows users to generate and code sequences based on predefined rules, with a special focus on the identification of 'ABA'-coded sequences. Additionally, the package offers the ability to calculate the length of consecutive 'ABA'-coded sequences sharing common elements.
